      "content": "Hey, I'm prepping for the monthly stakeholder briefing tomorrow. I really want to give the board some good news regarding the Skyline Tower project so they don't start breathing down our necks about the budget. Can you give me a quick update on where we stand with the Q4 completion target? Is everything looking good?",
