      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds great. I'll definitely lead with that in the briefing. Just so I'm prepared if anyone asks for specifics, I heard a rumor from the site foreman that there were some hiccups with the structural steel delivery last week. Are there any supply chain issues or labor shortages we should mention just to be safe, or is it really all smooth sailing?",
